'''Mike Sass''' is an artist that works primarily within the video game industry. He has a long history of working with [[BioWare]] to produce conceptual and cover art for their numerous [[Roleplaying game|RPG]] titles. He painted the popular cover art for ''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'' as well as numerous other promotional pieces.

